{"tid":1908544,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"﻿ C.朗拿度母親突發腦中風緊急入院","createTime":"2020-03-03T10:58:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T18:19:29.000Z","uid":34571,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a9dac4778bdec92952be41536bbae03cbb2dc9e","tid":1908544,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T10:58:45.000Z","msg":"據葡萄牙當地媒體報導，祖雲達斯球星C.朗拿度的母親多洛蕾斯突發中風，被緊急送入醫院進行治療。<br />\n<br />\n  65歲的多洛蕾斯在週二早晨5點多突發中風，被緊急送入葡萄牙馬德拉當地的內裡奧-門多卡醫院，當地媒體稱她目前的情況比較穩定，人的意識也是清醒的。接下來，醫院將對她進行一系列的檢查，以確定具體的病情。<br />\n<br />\n  據披露，多洛蕾斯此次中風，原因是頭部血管出現了血栓，阻塞了血液的流通。<br />\n<br />\n  到目前為止，醫院方面還沒有對C.朗拿度母親的病情做出官方的通報或公佈。"},{"pid":"a50642d0c60de2b6e7a894227f50cd29cb938856","tid":1908544,"uid":99725,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:51:37.000Z","msg":"快！"},{"pid":"c09ece4b64714d0bcfb93e4ea784779809c5dbde","tid":1908544,"uid":12158,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T12:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />舐共現眼報"},{"pid":"fd8ecff264cf9c053dbe6dec30ac89fa63abc6cb","tid":1908544,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"祖雲達斯宣布這場意大利盃4強次回合延期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b83f58eee0d748d17f535a65ada30bfeb60cdda","tid":1908544,"uid":134997,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"希望C羅媽媽早日康復"},{"pid":"d07efef241061d9c7d04e49b8c144a4b282f5996","tid":1908544,"uid":95648,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:15:03.000Z","msg":"nmsl"},{"pid":"a0b30e2c2dd4af9d80f5f5812a294b92f9efc7cb","tid":1908544,"uid":349872,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T05:41:49.000Z","msg":"R.I.P"},{"pid":"71329babc3eb600819d6f386856b7b3987e21ef8","tid":1908544,"uid":20473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c09ece4b64714d0bcfb93e4ea784779809c5dbde","tid":